  "translations": {
    "en": "Ahmad ibn Yahya al-Mukattib narrated to us. He said: Abu al-Tayyib Ahmad ibn Muhammad al-Warraq narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn Durayd al-Azdi al-Umani narrated to us. He said: al-Abbas ibn al-Faraj al-Riyashi narrated to us. He said: Abu Zayd al-Nahwi al-Ansari narrated to me. He said: I asked al-Khalil ibn Ahmad al-Arudi,",
